To '''fry''' [[food]] is to [[cook]] it in hot [[butter]] or [[vegetable oil]]. We can fry food in a small amount of butter or oil in a [[frying pan|pan]] or in a lot of oil in a [[pot]]. Some [[restaurant]]s also have large [[deep fryer]]s to fry a lot of food at once.


