The word '''good''' can be an [[adjective]] that means something that is [[want]]ed. Something that is good is not [[wikt:bad|bad]]. See [[wikt:good|good]] in the dictionary.
'''Good''' can also mean: *Good and [[Evil]], a concept in [[religion]] and [[philosophy]]. *[[Good (economics)]], something that is useful. *[[Good (philosophy)]], something that is valuable or important
